                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-07/debates/d6fbba64-1c67-4684-ad39-88a346e3f100/HealthAndCareBill(FirstSitting)"><u>First sitting: Col. [1-34</u></a><u>]</u> </p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-07/debates/5f1c2d5d-146c-4e94-ad81-f18ff6ec60d1/HealthAndCareBill(SecondSitting)"><u>Second sitting: Col. [35-84</u></a><u>]</u></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-09/debates/e2e6d5ba-a4a3-44ec-8926-4cd100069699/HealthAndCareBill(ThirdSitting)"><u>Third sitting: Col. [85-112</u></a><u>]</u> </p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-09/debates/815c3c99-3b0a-464b-8c70-54e42597c6c8/HealthAndCareBill(FourthSitting)"><u>Fourth sitting: Col. [113-168</u></a><u>]</u> </p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-14/debates/691aa8f4-0ef4-48ad-9c7a-e8c6dc361728/HealthAndCareBill(FifthSitting)"><u>Fifth sitting: Col. [169-204</u></a><u>]</u> </p>
